No. 1490,

Misc.

De la Cruz-Martinez v. Immigration and Naturalization Service. Stella Gramer for petitioner. Solicitor General Grisivold, Assistant Attorney General Wilson, and Philip R. Monahan for respondent.

C. A. 9th Cir. Cer-tiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Fortas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted.
